panels.description:
Load failure count - Total number of times the cache lookup method failed to compile a new script for the session with engine.

Load failure rate - Ratio of script compilation attempts that failed for the session with engine.

panels.description:
Eviction Count - Number of times a script compiled to a class has been evicted from the cache for the session with engine.

Eviction weight - Sum of the weights of evicted entries from the class cache for the session with engine.
